  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You assume a stance meant for your blade to block and your body to swiftly avoid incoming blows, until the start of your next turn you gain a +4 to your AC and when you are hit by an attack, reduce the incoming damage by your Strength modifier (maximum 5).</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank increase the cost of this jutsu by 3. If you cast this jutsu at B-Rank you instead reduce damage by twice your Strength modifier (max 10). If this jutsu is cast at S-Rank, you instead reduce incoming damage by your weapon's damage.</p>",
